  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will focus child-centred services (CCS) and education activities. Overall  Save the Children&apos;s response in the education sector will have a wide municipal reach. The above areas were identified together with the Regional Education Cluster as priority for clearing operations and resumption of classes given the impact on the communities and the need to show rapid resumption of school as a first step to recovery. Additionally  they are visible to the broader community and will act as a catalyst for other schools and communities.</narrative>
